==English==

===Noun===
'''spectacles''' ''plural''
# plural of [[spectacle]].
# {{pluralonly}} A pair of [[lens]]es set in a frame worn on the nose and ears in order to correct deficiencies in [[eyesight]] or to ornament the face.

====Synonyms====
*[[eyeglasses]] {{US}}
*[[glasses]]
*[[pair of eyeglasses]] {{US}}
*[[pair of glasses]]
*[[pair of specs]] {{colloquial}}
*[[pair of spectacles]]
*[[specs]] {{colloquial}}

